<h2>What Does the Fursona Sticker Switcher Do?</h2>
<p>
    If allows you to define one <strong>Image Source</strong> in OBS Studio or
    StreamLabs OBS, and swap out the image by clicking on the desired replacement
    image (or tapping on it, if you have a touchscreen device.)
</p>
